<description>
    <p>An arrow points somewhere and you have to find out where exactly.</p>
    <p>There are two games with different levels. You will have arrows with different colors and boxes with different colors to identify. There are several types of flying modes for the arrows, too.</p>
    <p>More information:</p>
    <ol>
        <li>Written in FreeBasic.</li>
        <li>Level codes to access the next level.</li>
        <li>Available for the web (https://maerchenfeeimgarten.codeberg.page/pfeilspiel/), Linux, Windows and DOS.</li>
        <li>Bad programming style ;-) Most of its code was written before I learn to program in a good way - and now I do not have enough time to fix it...</li>
        <li>Hosted on Codeberg. Mirrored to GitHub.</li>
        <li>Translated to German, English and French language.</li>
        <li>Smooth animations.</li>
    </ol>
</description>
